In the past 200 years of palaeontology. There’s been some pretty incorrect educated guesses about dinos. There’s also been completely wrong  wild guesses, and shots in the dark that fully missed the mark. But it’s all part of learning so let’s celebrate those mistakes and see some of the dinos we got completely wrong.
